name: Render Network
reason: The standard for decentralized GPU rendering. High utility, though carries some historical VC baggage.

name: Nosana
reason: Focused AI inference grid. Cleaner distribution than competitors. Represents true productive capacity.

name: Shadow Token
reason: Decentralized storage and RPC layer. Critical infrastructure built by engineers, not marketers.

name: Aleph.im
reason: Cross-chain indexing and compute middleware. A working product with steady utilization.

name: io.net
reason: High utility hardware, but polluted by excessive VC allocation and aggressive vesting cliffs. Extraction vehicle.

name: Akash Network (Wormhole)
reason: The Airbnb of Cloud Compute. Imported via Wormhole. Solid utility, standard bridge risk tariff.

name: Synesis One
reason: Crowdsourced RLHF data for AI. 'Data Farming' utility. Moderate tariff due to smaller cap volatility.

name: UpRock
reason: Unused bandwidth sharing for AI scraping. 'Fairer' distribution model via mobile mining.

name: Grass
reason: High-hype bandwidth scraping. Tokenomics lean heavily towards early insiders and points-farming dilution.
